\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The "Hobby" Tier:
\f0\b0  Free, but branded.\
\ls5\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The "Pro" Tier:
\f0\b0  $19/mo. Unlimited forms, no branding.\
\ls5\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The "Usage" Add-on:
\f0\b0  Instead of "Gold/Silver" tiers, charge a flat $0.05 per submission after the first 500. It's fairer and scales with the user.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
