\cf2 This architecture focuses on 
\f1\b Data Residency
\f0\b0  (keeping everything in Canada) and 
\f1\b Multi-tenancy
\f0\b0  (isolating customer data while keeping costs low).\
In 2026, the industry standard for a secure, scalable form-builder is the 
\f1\b "Pool Model with Row-Level Security (RLS)"
\f0\b0  for standard users, with an optional 
\f1\b "Silo"
\f0\b0  path for high-security enterprise or government clients.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

