\f1\b\fs28 \cf2 \strokec2 2. The Multi-Tenant Database Schema (PostgreSQL)\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf2 For a form builder, your database needs to handle 
\f1\b Form Definitions
\f0\b0  (the layout) and 
\f1\b Submissions
\f0\b0  (the answers). Using 
\f1\b JSONB
\f0\b0  allows you to store any form structure without needing a new table for every form.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

