\f1\b\fs28 \cf2 \strokec2 4. Critical Canadian Compliance Features\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf2 To satisfy 
\f1\b \cf2 \strokec2 PIPEDA
\f0\b0 \cf2 \strokec2  and 
\f1\b \cf2 \strokec2 Quebec's Law 25
\f0\b0 \cf2 \strokec2 , your architecture must include:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Encryption at Rest (KMS):
\f0\b0  Every tenant should have a unique Encryption Key (managed via AWS KMS in Canada) so that even a database dump is useless without the specific tenant's key.\
\ls9\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Audit Logs:
\f0\b0  A separate, immutable table that logs every time an admin views a submission.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa160\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl1
\f2\i \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	
\f4\i0 \uc0\u9702 
\f2\i 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Columns: \cf6 \cb8 \strokec6 timestamp\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 , \cf6 \cb8 \strokec6 admin_user_id\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 , \cf6 \cb8 \strokec6 submission_id\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 , \cf6 \cb8 \strokec6 action\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 .
\f0\i0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
\ls9\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Right to Erasure (Hard Delete):
\f0\b0  Unlike JotForm, which sometimes keeps "soft deletes," your app should offer a "Provable Wipe" feature for sensitive Canadian records.\
\ls9\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	4	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Data-Locality Guardrails:
\f0\b0  Use AWS Service Control Policies (SCPs) to physically prevent any data from being moved or backed up to a US-based region (like us-east-1).\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

